<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <title>盛香亭 | 每日晚报表计算生成应用</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.bootcdn.net/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/floating-labels.css" />

    <!-- 如果浏览器版本为IE8以下，使用coliff/bootstrap-ie8替代Bootstrap4 -->
    <!--[if IE 9]>
      <link
        href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/coliff/bootstrap-ie8/css/bootstrap-ie9.min.css"
        rel="stylesheet"
      />
    <![endif]-->
    <!--[if lte IE 8]>
      <link
        href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/coliff/bootstrap-ie8/css/bootstrap-ie8.min.css"
        rel="stylesheet"
      />
      <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/g/html5shiv@3.7.3"></script>
    <![endif]-->
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        font-family: "Microsoft YaHei";
      }

      h2 {
        margin-bottom: 2px;
        font-weight: normal;
      }

      .container {
        width: auto;
        max-width: 680px;
        padding-bottom: 40px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="mt-4">欢迎使用！</h2>
      <br />
      <p>请打开门店手机，准确填写相应数据。完成后点击提交。</p>
      <form action="/" method="post">
        <label><b>美团外卖</b>：</label>
        <div class="input-group input-group-sm mb-3">
          <div class="form-label-group">
            <input type="number" step="0.01" name="meituan_sales" id="meituan_sales" class="form-control" placeholder="美团外卖销售额" required /> <label for="meituan_sales">美团外卖销售额</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-label-group">
            <input type="number" step="1" name="meituan_amount" id="meituan_amount" class="form-control" placeholder="美团外卖单数" required />
            <label for="meituan_amount">美团外卖单数</label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <label><b>美团开店宝</b>：</label>
        <div class="input-group input-group-sm mb-3">
          <div class="form-label-group">
            <input type="number" step="0.01" name="kaidianbao_sales" id="kaidianbao_sales" class="form-control" placeholder="开店宝销售额" required />
            <label for="kaidianbao_sales">开店宝销售额</label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <label><b>口碑掌柜</b>：</label>
        <div class="input-group input-group-sm mb-3">
          <div class="form-label-group">
            <input type="number" step="0.01" name="koubei_sales" id="koubei_sales" class="form-control" placeholder="口碑销售额" required />
            <label for="koubei_sales">口碑销售额</label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p>全部填写完成后，点击提交进入下一步。</p>

        <label><b>昨日</b>累计营业额（账本记录）：</label>
        <div class="input-group input-group-sm mb-3">
          <div class="form-label-group">
            <input type="number" step="0.01" name="yesterday_all_sales" id="yesterday_all_sales" class="form-control" placeholder="昨日累计营业额"
            />
            <label for="yesterday_all_sales">昨日累计营业额</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-label-group">
            <input type="number" name="yesterday_all_amount" id="yesterday_all_amount" class="form-control" placeholder="昨日累计GC" />
            <label for="xiaochengxu_sells">昨日累计GC</label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">提交</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>